{"tid":1590470,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動/文宣]930三罷 自動戒嚴 國慶前一日淪為死城","createTime":"2019-09-23T17:24:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T15:03:55.000Z","uid":70973,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"cf40d2d597fbe159d0e0966bdb692485073542da","tid":1590470,"uid":70973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:24:35.000Z","msg":"928 929遊行後，請以三罷接力，連街都唔好出，你當用黎訓教，準備10.1送大禮，務求新聞頭條係&quot;<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港國慶前一日淪為死城</span></span></strong>&quot;<br />\n如果真係想連玩4日，和理非可以去連儂/大街貼各國國旗，食完早餐十點零十一點到集會既商場鳩嗚唱下歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />;而勇武最好唔好去做&rdquo;被罷工&rdquo;工作，多休息，到時10.1腳仔軟仲on9<br />\n<br />\n各位請射一放四<br />\n本身有唔少人拎左930假，玩連假去旅行，班港豬就變相幫手罷工+掩護罷工，同相對較易影響日常運作<br />\n支共大壽前既交易日實做靚個市，搞個三罷增加佢托市成本都好<br />\n以下係拋磚引玉既文宣圖，自問太廢:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KaTwJCr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKaTwJCr.png&h=9d516b44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nap71o6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnap71o6.png&h=de524756&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k4PWUJ7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk4PWUJ7.png&h=da7183e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mirrormedia.com.tw/assets/images/20190802155848-6795b8e67c3325de708034f736183bf5-mobile.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.com.tw%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F20190802155848-6795b8e67c3325de708034f736183bf5-mobile.jpg&h=354d35fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係針對藍屍既(膠)文宣圖，拋磚引玉，自問太廢:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5mJwHid.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5mJwHid.png&h=6ac8ea34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x4R6v57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx4R6v57.jpg&h=4b2ef1f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係口號/文宣素材:<br />\n九月三十工作多, 香港市民要甩拖<br />\n930 工作多, 香港人要射波<br />\n930, 變死城<br />\n返工返學障礙多, 留喺屋企唱榮光<br />\n罷工罷市唔鬼鼠, 輕輕鬆鬆做港豬"},{"pid":"597cee3a26ebaabd64a89b22d0edeffa5ca647f3","tid":1590470,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:24:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"2fcf8f321885e38ba20cb239abcc2b206853827d","tid":1590470,"uid":70973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:25:18.000Z","msg":"930, 變死城"},{"pid":"8cde033b41eca49e273c7e01479020141e7ff1ad","tid":1590470,"uid":70973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:25:48.000Z","msg":"返工返學障礙多, 留喺屋企唱榮光"},{"pid":"4fdba76515ac51b433ab4b1fa57a86a2ed91c18d","tid":1590470,"uid":70973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:25:59.000Z","msg":"罷工罷市唔鬼鼠, 輕輕鬆鬆做港豬"},{"pid":"8ed3775fb6dc7d5b7006717e0c5e330623f7d082","tid":1590470,"uid":70973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:26:21.000Z","msg":"930 工作多, 香港人要射波"},{"pid":"46f16d3cf71f3931b0cc6582df69a9a48b0a1c00","tid":1590470,"uid":70973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:27:18.000Z","msg":"難得射一放四本身已經一堆人拎假同大家都唔會有咩心機做野返工意志減低既日子<br />\n點解唔試？"},{"pid":"36cae6fd9f5541ddd157d3f51edaafbbf0e576cb","tid":1590470,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a1d2478971e11355cad233bc6b79bce3af58e35","tid":1590470,"uid":23104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T18:04:31.000Z","msg":"三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" cla